<s-1 id="RM000000Z28002X_01_0005" proc-id="RM0250U___00004FA00000">
<ptxt>INSTALL FRONT DIFFERENTIAL RING GEAR</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Using a heater, heat the front differential ring gear to 90 to 100°C (194.0 to 212.0°F).</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C092888E03" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Clean the surface that contacts the differential case.</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Aligning the matchmarks, quickly install the front differential ring gear to the front differential case.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C070796E01" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<torque>
<torqueitem>
<t-value1>106</t-value1>
<t-value2>1,081</t-value2>
<t-value4>78</t-value4>
</torqueitem>
</torque>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
<s-1 id="RM000000Z28002X_01_0006" proc-id="RM0250U___00004FB00000">
<ptxt>INSTALL SPEEDOMETER DRIVE GEAR</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Install the speedometer drive gear to the front differential case.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C070795" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
</s2>
</content1>
